bio.singa.structure.model.identifiers

Class LeafIdentifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • bio.singa.structure.model.identifiers.LeafIdentifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<LeafIdentifier>

    public class LeafIdentifier
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<LeafIdentifier>
    The leaf identifier consists of the PDB identifer, the model identifier, the chain identifier, the serial of a leaf substructure and optionally its insertion code.
